methods.caseInsensitiveValueOf:
Retrieves the enum constant whose name matches a given value according to case-insensitive comparison.

Note: Java generics information - <T extends java.lang.Enum<?>>

:param enumClass: (java.lang.Class<T>) - the enum type we are querying
:param value: (java.lang.String) - the constant value we are looking up
:return: (T) the enum constant
